<section id="To_generate_widget_content_immediately" remap="TID_15443">
	<title>Generating Widget Content Immediately</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Generate Widget Content Immediately</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Cloud Intelligence</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reports</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the <guimenu>Dashboard Widgets</guimenu> accordion and select the widget you want to generate.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Configuration)</guibutton>, and then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Generate Widget Content now)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<formalpara>
		<title>Result:</title>
		<para>
			The content is generated immediately instead of waiting for the next scheduled update. Generation of widget content is shown under the <guisubmenu>Tasks</guisubmenu> page of 
			<inlinemediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata fileref="images/1846.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Settings &amp; Operations)</guibutton>.
		</para>
	</formalpara>
</section>